# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and working tree. jj snapshots
# (and Nova's edit tool) always write LF, so storing LF keeps git, jj, and the
# working tree in agreement — otherwise every edit churns the whole file's line
# endings and jj/git fight on checkout. Binary files are auto-detected and left
# untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
